      Classes in org.pircbotx.hooks.managers that implement ListenerManager 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  BackgroundListenerManager
      A standard ThreadListenerManager with dedicated background threads.
      class  GenericListenerManager<E extends PircBotX>
      Deprecated. 
      Due to multiple new functions of PircBotX theat depend on multiple threads, this class is deprecated and is only kept for legacy reasons or special cases. Use of this class will have unexpected results. All bots should now use ThreadedListenerManager.
      class  ThreadedListenerManager<E extends PircBotX>
      Wraps a ListenerManager and adds multithreading to ThreadedListenerManager.dispatchEvent(org.pircbotx.hooks.Event).
